    "is_free": false,
    "description": "请注意：2-4人分屏模式需要控制器。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/21e3514d038e92fcf782c8dd620bd3db.webp?t=1727089497\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>扮演比尔、玛珠、洛奇、泰妮和更多巨太龙朋友。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/1cdb8434d9ca5e54ec740e808a045b2b.poster.avif?t=1727089497\" width=600 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/1cdb8434d9ca5e54ec740e808a045b2b.webm?t=1727089497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在最多支持4位各年龄段玩家的史前卡丁车锦标赛中，围绕克里塔西亚展开竞赛，玩家可在其中扮演自己最喜爱的恐龙朋友，甚至可能与神秘的巨太龙本尊不期而遇！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/8bf7d6a0a359d6ca23957e75d1ae51e9.webp?t=1727089497\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>最多支持4位玩家分屏竞逐<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/3243ec0e612802fba2db50b5fe3d81cc.poster.avif?t=1727089497\" width=600 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/3243ec0e612802fba2db50b5fe3d81cc.webm?t=1727089497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>这场赛车冒险中充满唯有恐龙世界才能找到的精彩障碍和强化。玩家要逃离诸如遗忘山灼热熔岩喷发之类的危险，或感受鼎鼎大名的巨太龙咆哮的威力。通过拾取特殊技能为自己开辟捷径，或拾取喷气背包动力强化……或是得到某种击败对手的方法，让你冲到车队最前头。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/a11cbc9b1d1ca7f66bb35cd4f79340ab.webp?t=1727089497\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>在萨凡纳、丛林和遗忘山杯的15条赛道上竞逐<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/b84f6894523e3f8adf81fc3d9a81b11c.poster.avif?t=1727089497\" width=600 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/b84f6894523e3f8adf81fc3d9a81b11c.webm?t=1727089497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>每种能力水平都有适合的游戏风格，包括自动转向卡丁车和甲龙玛珠大声读出屏幕文字功能。游戏中共有15条赛道和8名角色可供选择，整个恐龙赛车世界正等着你来发现。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/400b6047c8656413eac0a43d7f3d3b09.webp?t=1727089497\" width=615 height=54 /></span><br><br>利用自动转向和玛珠的阅读帮助功能，各年龄段的恐龙都有机会获胜<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/2fd0748560b86791a6ca74fe92d50318.poster.avif?t=1727089497\" width=600 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770500/extras/2fd0748560b86791a6ca74fe92d50318.webm?t=1727089497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>所以，快让全家人聚到一起，开一场节奏明快、妙趣横生、规模大到犹如巨太龙胃口的派对吧！",
